Transcription.Text: The small rocket craft, for destroying big ships, are controlled automatically, even to the preparations for launching their rockets. Red NATO. Applauding on the river banks at Leningrad were thousands now told that in 20 years they will have free food, Housing, light, heat, transport and medical treatment - all for a working week of 34 to 36 hours.
